38590,"uid":83368,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:49:13.000Z","msg":"其實無贏過，嗌下口號貼下文宣就會贏，洗撚要軍隊咩<br />\n<br />\n港共就係知道依點，攬實警隊咪夠囉<br />\n<br />\n口講無輸無輸，精神勝利法"},{"pid":"b0c12a5e02ef2bc78494921e41feb28a5346a197","tid":1838590,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:51:10.000Z","msg":"你應該諗，點樣借呢場運動去煽動大家仇恨中國、推冚中國"},{"pid":"5de925b91e562021999758bb280180be691e8d47","tid":1838590,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"呢啲po，就係點解愈黎愈少人上連登既原因。<br />\n<br />\n品葱既手足從來冇擔心過香港人會放棄。"},{"pid":"2bf6cfd045269910187d20f2dbced52b27147bc4","tid":1838590,"uid":70745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5de925b91e562021999758bb280180be691e8d47","tid":1838590,"uid":281401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"呢啲po，就係點解愈黎愈少人上連登既原因。<br />\n<br />\n品葱既手足從來冇擔心過香港人會放棄。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n<br />\n拉"},{"pid":"70688a2fea6047040cd687188b8c2ec0aac9d085","tid":1838590,"uid":54564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"覺得運動會完嘅只有你"},{"pid":"068a83db263fa1e7548c240cb20f5ef5a2cbfaf6","tid":1838590,"uid":43322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:54:57.000Z","msg":"2019-20 擺脫左14佔路=抗爭既思想<br />\n但始終擺脫唔到上街=抗爭既心態"},{"pid":"86a042a132863c08e2430de176ad69f40635e219","tid":1838590,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70688a2fea6047040cd687188b8c2ec0aac9d085","tid":1838590,"uid":54564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"覺得運動會完嘅只有你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T05:55:21.000Z","msg":"覺得運動會完嘅只有你（樓主）"},{"pid":"9d6d31167a74d240f33a2af483f1c0b17093844d","tid":1838590,"uid":83368,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"70688a2fea6047040cd687188b8c2ec0aac9d085","tid":1838590,"uid":54564,"like":1,"dislike":